column5: May those that are heading out to draw back the string,shoot straight and happy harvesting to you all. A safe bow season to all.   Looking forward to some great reports

I Just tried to just buy the Diamond Justice this past weekend. But sadly they didn't have a shorter draw length module  - I hope to have the bow by this weekend:D if I can get my hands the DB5, DB6.  Can't wait to see the reports!
Get me some antlers,   Bri! (I just shoot paper deer with my bow nowadays.)
I,ll try bud,but with getting drawn with an anterless tag,the ol saying comes up, IF IT,S BROWN,IT,S DOWN.
Dang! Where I'm from it's "Once black..never look back!"
Good Luck Everybody!  Can't wait to see the hunting reports!
Anyone know any places where I can get my hunting license? Anywhere from Hamilton- Sauga? and how long it could take?
